<a href="/articles/24685.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/24685/indexMediumPc2/24685.jpg?1459302188" alt="今日娱乐：黄磊主演《深夜食堂》，伍迪又为戛纳开幕">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/3/medium/3.png?1411569578" alt="娱乐">
			<span>娱乐</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">今日娱乐：黄磊主演《深夜食堂》，伍迪又为戛纳开幕</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-30 09:57:20 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">6</span>
